        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer36216370" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8853976652674209994">Did not like it. Although it has an interesting structure and pretext, it is so intellectualized that it is hard to care about the characters at all. It seems like Frazier is more interested in showing off than in writing a gripping work of fiction. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


