      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/7130.Charles_Frazier">About Charles Frazier</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/7130.Charles_Frazier"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1316568662p3/7130.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/7130.Charles_Frazier">Charles Frazier
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
1,318
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer15672677909344970030">Charles Frazier is an award-winning author of American historical fiction. His literary corpus, to date, is comprised of three New York Times best selling novels: <i>Nightwoods</i> (2011), <i>Thirteen Moons</i> (2006), and <i>Cold Mountain</i> (1997) - winner of the National Book Award for Fiction.<br/><br/><br/><i>Librarian Note: There are multiple authors in the goodreads database with this name. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/44217-master-list-of-author-disambiguation-by-spaces' rel='nofollow noopener'>more info here.</a></i> </span>
  <span id="freeText15672677909344970030" style="display:none">Charles Frazier is an award-winning author of American historical fiction. His literary corpus, to date, is comprised of three New York Times best selling novels: <i>Nightwoods</i> (2011), <i>Thirteen Moons</i> (2006), and <i>Cold Mountain</i> (1997) - winner of the National Book Award for Fiction.<br /><br /><br /><i>Librarian Note: There are multiple authors in the goodreads database with this name. <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/44217-master-list-of-author-disambiguation-by-spaces" rel="nofollow noopener">more info here.</a></i> </span>
  <a data-text-id="15672677909344970030" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
